data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is set on a quiet, dead-end street, perfectly placed between Caledonia Schools and Columbus shopping. Features: huge, 1.2 acre fenced-in yard with covered patio and three storage buildings ~ whole house propane generator ~ living room, large den and kitchen with breakfast bar and dining area ~ laundry/mud room ~ new shower in hall bath with extra support bars ~ great storage throughout ~ 2 car garage
